<event name="GB_STOREEVENT_FED_VOLUNTEER" unique="true">
	<preventQuest/>
	<beaconType id="map_icon_store_federation" global="false">
		<color r="215" g="255" b="200" a="1"/>
	</beaconType>
	<text>One of the few systems in this sector that still has a heavy Federation presence. Bristling with concealed firing positions all over the surrounding moons and allied patrols.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Access the market.</text>
		<event load="GB_STORE_LOAD_FED"/>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Volunteer to stand guard for a while for pay.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Federation soldiers are glad to take a break, and the warden agrees to let you stand guard. Your shift will take one jump cycle, shouldn't be too hard with such heavy support at this facility.</text>
